.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2025中国製造都打撚殘晒你哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"我個人認為要不斷向外宣傳我国嘅2025中国製造，好畀西方一個落馬威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f65d0fc34869d48baafed7b072c75095ea8dc78","tid":798470,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:38:02.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係中國固有利益家族<br />\n聯合美帝逼習帝落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb439396cd598938215119d958ee0ef9935a015","tid":798470,"uid":163350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11914d09f0cef71c46db90593312fc24f627f4a4","tid":798470,"uid":121146,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"還記得侵侵選到既時候個個話美國孤立自己  實玩完<br />\n點知侵帝憑一人之力  居然可以重建世界新秩序<br />\n美國選到一個咁強勁既總統真係人類之福<br />\n我敢講本身支共真係有機會2025<br />\n但侵帝一野就打返佢落無間地獄  美國國運最少長多五十年"},{"pid":"4738658ba62de6494e4a05c2ac4ffa34976a6aad","tid":798470,"uid":163350,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7009a24fa5b6b7770c7194c2ba7962bafc13b1e","tid":798470,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ac71809a16033f4a2ebbdd7f82733292e7d41cd","tid":798470,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ab6f74d959e298b7dd920fd1a40cb6002256b8e","tid":798470,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"03ea162e26b1d0a3abe5669c5af2dd66ff52eb5e","tid":798470,"uid":176366,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:24:20.000Z","msg":"你班傻鳩打夠飛機未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face